data.title: Is Punisher: War Zone part of the MCU?
data.meta_description: Answer (1 of 5): Although Punisher: War Zone (2008) was co-produced by Marvel Studios and released half a year after the first MCU film, Iron Man (2008), the company does not consider it to be part of its Marvel Cinematic Universe and does not list it among the Marvel Movies | Marvel Cinematic Un...
